## Best Practices
1. Use Poetry for dependency management
2. Maintain separate dependency groups
3. Pin dependency versions
4. Use semantic versioning
5. Keep lock files updated
6. Document dependency purposes
7. Use virtual environments
8. Regular dependency updates
9. Security vulnerability checks
10. Maintain clean dependency tree

